<meta name="keywords" content="IPD IPDB Internet Pinball Machine Database Game Bally Classic Payout Machine 1 ball for 5 cents. Scoring bumpers (23). Spinning bumper (advertised here as a 'whirling bumper', it is the bottom-most red-colored bumper on the playfield). Steel playfield. Projection score. Electronic tubes in main cabinet. Game advertised as 54 inches long by 26 inches wide.  ">
